jchess.cache

Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • jchess.cache.Path
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPath, IPathAgent, IPathData

    public final class Path
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPathData, IPathAgent
    This is a data class to store "Path or Direction" related details in cache. It actually maps XML or DB structure for "Path or Direction" to memory.

    7 Dec 2019
    Author:
